_sText: This map has many secrets but about the same amount of traps. be cautious when pressing buttons its kind of a guessing game in some places. I added alot more to my orignal map "Lucky city" and better spots but i believe none of them are impossible! I checked every spot and made a few adjustments. This map was made more for game play then realism. If you have any notes or ideas for this map i would like to hear em.
